data.description: Beautiful property located in Polk city. A quiet and cozy place that features 5 acres (completely fenced). There is enough space for animals! There are chicken coops in perfect condition, with different divisions.   This property is on two floors and measures 1,828 sq ft. It has three bedrooms and two and a half bathrooms.   Also features a very large bonus/game room on the first floor.  Home has been recently painted and with the new roof (2021) and Air-conditioning (2020; with 10-year warranty).  This house is completely furnished with solar panels throughout the entire house!!  You can relax outside on its large terrace and monitor the entire property. Great location to visit all of parks in Orlando (Just 17 minutes from World Disney world). Make your appointment today!!! Thank you!!!!
